RollCallVoteResults.InformationNote.text:p: Corrections to votes appear in the section relating to the vote concerned.
For any comments relating to corrections to votes or voting intentions, please see the corresponding item in the minutes.

Corrections to votes submitted before 18.30 will be included. Any corrections received within a maximum of two weeks after that time will appear in the electronic version of this annex, which will be updated on a regular basis.
Once the two-week deadline has passed, the list of corrections to votes will be finalised with a view to publication in the Official Journal.
